title: Tamannaah’s fan moment with SRK
text: Shah Rukh Khan is on a roll. The Bollywood actor recently visited the set of Mahesh Babu and Ram Charan's upcoming films. With the Tollywood stars gushing about meeting SRK, the latest to talk about the actor is Tamannaah, who recently shot for a commercial with him. The pretty actress posted a picture with him on her Instagram account and captioned it saying, "My fan moment #sharukhkhan he is a total inspiration, had the most awesome time at shoot." The duo shot for an online fashion portal and it seemed like the actress had a lot of fun on the set. The actress is presently working on Nagarajuna-Karthi starrer, Thozha.
